We stress that in the limit of infinitely large supercell the
coupling with the background gives no contribution to the
computed U, but we found that this limit is approached more
rapidly when this additional degree of freedom is included.
In the same spirit we found that the spatial locality of the
response matrices can be rather different from the one of
their inverse and a supercell sufficient to decouple the peri-
