however, not examined in detail in the present work and their
analysis remain for further studies.
IV. EXAMPLES
A. Metals: Iron and cerium
In their seminal paper Anisimov and Gunnarsson8 com-
puted the effective on site Coulomb interaction between the
localized electrons in metallic Fe and Ce. For Ce the calcu-
